So the Library of Congress
was originally located

00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:43.770
in this space.

00:08:43.770 --> 00:08:45.930
And it is indeed difficult

00:08:45.930 --> 00:08:49.650
to overstate the
importance of that space.

00:08:49.650 --> 00:08:53.680
By the way, today, and for many
years, it has been the offices

00:08:53.680 --> 00:08:55.470
of the Republican
Senate leadership.

00:08:55.470 --> 00:08:58.710
Of course, today is
